description: HP's Smokehouse BBQ is a BBQ truck serving the streets of Kirkland and the surrounding areas. The menu includes savory wood-smoked pulled pork sandwiches, baby back ribs, chicken breast sandwiches, hot links, and beef brisket, all enhanced with HP's smokehouse BBQ sauce, and accompanied by a delicious downhome side. If this description has already set your tummy rumbling, check out HP's today!
name: HP's Smokehouse BBQ
